metadata.name: ADA_GARDEN-d0100
metadata.description:
"Because the golden north opens to the west, the clouds gather there on the night side. The sun is never set. The air is always clean and clear.
There is no reality
This is the land of fiction. Everything is just a dream.
I don't know about their technology but it's the first thing I have ever read about this world that sounds realistic.
Does it have to be a dream?
You can't see your own body?"
